text: The three-toed worm lizard (Bipes tridactylus) is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is endemic to Mexico. ==References== Category:Bipes (lizard) Category:Reptiles of Mexico Category:Endemic fauna of Mexico Category:Taxa named by Alfredo Dugès Category:Reptiles described in 1894
title: Three-toed worm lizard
